{%- comment -%}MTW Educator Header — wagon logo + brand + nav. Hides retail chrome, retail apps, Shop-AI launcher, rewards launchers (Smile/Yotpo/LoyaltyLion), and chat widgets (Klaviyo/Gorgias/Tidio/Drift/Intercom/Crisp).{%- endcomment -%}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500;1,600&family=Mulish:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
